===Ba gua===
{{Main|Ba gua}}
The movements have also been correlated to the eight trigrams of the [[I Ching]]:
{| class=&quot;wikitable&quot;
|-
! Movement|| Metal || Earth || Wood || Wood || Water || Fire || Earth || Metal
|-
! I Ching
