'''Cyril''' (also Cyrillus or Cyryl) is a masculine given name. It is derived from the [[Greek language|Greek]] name Κύριλλος (''Kyrillos'') meaning &quot;Lordly, Masterful&quot; which in turn derives from Greek κυριος (Kyrios) &quot;[[Lord]]&quot;. There are various variant forms of the Cyril name such as Cyrill, Kirill, Kiryl, Kirillos, Kyryl, Kiril, and Kyrill. There are also different ways of spelling the name Cyril for example it is spelt Cyryl in Poland.

It may also refer to:

* Saint [[Cyril of Jerusalem]], Patriarch of Jerusalem
* Saint [[Cyril of Alexandria]], Pope of the Church of Alexandria 
* [[Cyrillus]], 5th century Greek jurist
* [[Saints Cyril and Methodius]], 9th century Greek missionaries
* Saint [[Cyril of Turaw]], 12th century Belarusian Orthodox Christian bishop and theologian
* [[Cyril Lucaris]] (1572–1638), [[Ecumenical Patriarch of Constantinople]]
* Sir [[Cyril Burt]], 20th century psychologist
* [[Cyril Delevanti]] (1889–1975), British actor
* [[Cyril De Zoysa]], Sri Lankan businessman and Buddhist revivalist
* [[Cyril Toumanoff|Cyril Leo Heraclius, Prince Toumanoff (born Toumanishvili)]] (1913–1997), Russian-born historian and genealogist who was a Professor Emeritus at Georgetown University
* [[Cyril Stanley Harrison]], (1915 - 1998) English cricketer 
* Elder [[Cyril Pavlov]] (b. 1919), Russian Orthodox Christian monk, mystic and wonder-worker
* [[Cyril Smith]], British Liberal politician
* [[S. M. Cyril]], educational innovator in India
* [[Cyril Domoraud]] (b. 1971), Ivorian football player (senior career 1992&amp;ndash;2008) who played for the Côte d'Ivoire national team (1995&amp;ndash;2006) 
* [[Cyril Takayama]], Japanese American illusionist
* [[Cyril Kaye]], (b. 1983), 21st century Filipino-American radical Christ-follower/believer, contemporary graphic artist
* [[Cyril George]]
* Another name of [[Nikita the Furrier]]
* [[Cyril Sneer]], the fictional villain aardvark of the 1980s cartoon series ''[[The Raccoons]]''
* [[Cyril O'Reily]] fictional character from television series [[Oz (TV series)|Oz]]

