[[File:Cessna.195.300pix.jpg|right|thumb|1951 Cessna 195]]
[[Image:Cessna 337 Skymaster.jpg|right|thumb|Cessna 337 Skymaster, a &quot;[[Push-pull configuration|push-pull]]&quot; aircraft]]
